==Situation of the language== The [[Shabak people]] fear the demise of the Shabaki language especially after the occupation of the [[Islamic State of Iraq and the Levant|ISIS terrorist]] groups to their home in [[Nineveh plains|Nineveh plain]], which led to the displacement of the majority of their population and the other groups residing in that area.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://telegram7.com/?p=475|title=International Mother Language Day in Karbala, Iraq - Telegram7|date=2015-03-03|work=Telegram7|access-date=2018-10-26|language=en-US}}</ref>
